Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.49,0:00:04.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.05,0:00:06.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He can't be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.46,0:00:11.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I shot Akai Shuuichi with my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.45,0:00:23.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gin, it happened right in front of your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.49,0:00:26.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not in front of my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.03,0:00:27.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was through a monitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.16,0:00:32.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could have employed any number of tricks to fake it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.92,0:00:34.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong, Kir?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.63,0:00:39.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tricks?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.26,0:00:41.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of tricks could I use?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.84,0:00:47.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember, the one who ordered me to call\NAkai to Raiha Pass in the first place...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.43,0:00:48.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.68,0:00:49.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.77,0:00:50.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.73,0:00:52.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll call him now, right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:54.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.65,0:00:56.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's become difficult to stay in the Organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.36,0:01:00.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want your help to leave and fly out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.74,0:01:03.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, I'll offer any information that the FBI wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.28,0:01:06.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can we meet now, just the two of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.16,0:01:08.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.12,0:01:09.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It won't be a problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.95,0:01:10.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So long as you're alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.21,0:01:13.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:18.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was also you who ordered me to blow his head off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.26,0:01:23.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The head.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.97,0:01:27.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Drive a bullet right into his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.01,0:01:29.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That way we can be sure that his life...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.18,0:01:32.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Has come to a final end.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.77,0:01:37.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, you saw his blood pouring\Nout of his head while he collapsed...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.98,0:01:41.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Via the camera you installed on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.15,0:01:46.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After you rescued me from the FBI...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.74,0:01:49.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The organization constantly monitored me closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.49,0:01:52.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd have been impossible for me to contact him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.08,0:01:55.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no means of utilizing any sort of trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.87,0:02:04.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is, unless you're implying he or I had superhuman\Nbrainpower that allowed us to calculate that far ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.13,0:02:06.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe then we could have tricked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.22,0:02:09.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, like that of Sherlock Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.93,0:02:17.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about you put a stop to your baseless doubts\Nand just be happy that your nemesis is gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.61,0:02:21.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so overjoyed I can't contain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:24.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because if he were really alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.40,0:02:28.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could kill him all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.69,0:02:31.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Flowers dance to the piano's rhythm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.48,0:02:33.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two people face-to-face is a mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:35.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The time limit's drawing near.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:37.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Time for me to unearth the bomber's true intent!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.08,0:02:39.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.58,0:02:41.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.54,0:02:43.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.44,0:04:27.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A strange request arrived at the Mouri Detective Agency:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:32.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Someone wishes for you to solve the mystery of the\Nred T-shirts that have been sent every week...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.61,0:04:34.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"So please offer your expertise," it went.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.53,0:04:39.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We went to Beika Department Store to meet said person, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.45,0:04:43.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We encountered a man with bombs strapped around his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:50.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apparently, he was threatened by a masked man who\Nclaimed bombs had been planted all over the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.26,0:04:53.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It appeared we had become trapped on that same floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.55,0:05:00.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The masked man ordered that the sender\Nof the weekly red T-shirts be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:04.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He also said that the sender is on the very same floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:11.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We checked the 13 red T-shirts that were\Ncarried by the man with bombs on his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.69,0:05:13.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And from the enclosed receipts...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:21.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We learned that these were bought at the\Nfitness section every Sunday at 12:28 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.79,0:05:24.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who was the sender of the T-shirts?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.50,0:05:26.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is their intent?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:33.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, what is the identity of the bomber who\Ndemanded that the sender be found?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:47.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vodka, move the car opposite the department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.23,0:05:51.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get us in a position where we can see this\Nman who looks like Akai as he leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.57,0:05:54.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:56.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.15,0:05:57.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.66,0:05:58.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:02.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to Korn, who's watching the basement exit...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:06.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's apparently something going on inside the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.96,0:06:08.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Korn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.17,0:06:09.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got any details?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.71,0:06:13.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dunno, but I did see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.34,0:06:19.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A SWAT and bomb disposal team head in earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:22.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A SWAT and bomb disposal team?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:24.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.31,0:06:27.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:47.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, hold on a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.08,0:06:54.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm here to find the person among the customers on\Nthis floor that's been sending red shirts every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.05,0:06:57.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You do understand that this is per the bomber's request?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.63,0:06:59.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.47,0:07:03.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The receipts that were also sent were from this department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.51,0:07:08.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the only place the shirts are sold is here, in the fitness section.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.73,0:07:09.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even beyond that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:13.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were always purchased on Sundays at 12:28.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.61,0:07:18.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the salesperson in charge at this time on Sunday...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:21.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is you and you only, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.49,0:07:26.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, why is it you can't remember that customer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:29.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Normally you would remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:33.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since they've been coming to buy the\Nsame thing at the same time every week!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.25,0:07:35.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:37.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really don't remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.09,0:07:39.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:46.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I haven't sold any of that red underwear today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.22,0:07:51.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, did any other clerks happen to cover for you around that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.44,0:07:54.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one has covered for me in the past half year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:58.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, could this receipt be from a few years back?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:07:59.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.86,0:08:03.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We just started using that type of receipt earlier this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.28,0:08:10.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I always take the money and items from the customers...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.12,0:08:14.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And hand them over to the office of the cashier, Seta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.42,0:08:20.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, I bring the change and receipt along with\Nthe bagged items back to the waiting customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.97,0:08:27.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If there had been such a strange customer...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:30.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I doubt I'd forget someone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.35,0:08:32.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:35.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have the receipts proving they were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.69,0:08:37.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.82,0:08:40.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bomb man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:42.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't come any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.32,0:08:46.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, stop calling me the bomb man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.33,0:08:49.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not the bomber!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:52.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just someone who has been strapped with bombs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.79,0:08:55.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm an innocent, ordinary citizen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:08:58.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you hot hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.21,0:09:02.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you to stay away until I've solved the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:04.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.80,0:09:07.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the boy with glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:11.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's playing around with those red T-shirts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.56,0:09:13.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Playing around?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:25.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.70,0:09:27.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like you did earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.49,0:09:31.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I merely folded along the creases in the shirts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:37.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But they look creepy when you line them up, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:40.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, just like in that Holmes story...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.21,0:09:42.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The Dancing Men"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.63,0:09:45.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, right—they look like that code.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:48.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, maybe this is a code too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.14,0:09:51.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we read them from right to left in the order they were sent...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:52.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe a phrase will be formed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:57.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I take my eyes off of you for a bit and this is what happens!\NGeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.27,0:09:59.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.94,0:10:03.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you to behave?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.44,0:10:07.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} said that by folding along the creases in the shirts...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:10.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It might form a code.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.45,0:10:12.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A code?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:14.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't possibly be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.91,0:10:18.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way to tell when those creases were made!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:25.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:27.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sender of the red underwear?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.59,0:10:29.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.76,0:10:33.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems the bomber's aim is to find that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.56,0:10:35.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, do we know how many bombs?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.64,0:10:38.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to the surveillance cameras...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.85,0:10:41.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's one at each of the two elevators and each of the two stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.44,0:10:44.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Adding the upward and downward escalators...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:46.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're looking at six places at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Six places, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.99,0:10:50.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a hassle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.03,0:10:52.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.37,0:10:55.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For a bomber to hijack an entire floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:57.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They let too much information leak in such a short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.79,0:10:58.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.75,0:11:00.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.13,0:11:02.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.25,0:11:04.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're on the floor with the bombs?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.13,0:11:06.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, is it all right for you to be calling?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.67,0:11:08.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't the bomber there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.76,0:11:11.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems they haven't even taken the hostages' cell phones.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.43,0:11:14.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Think this is an amateur job?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.35,0:11:16.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:19.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot, quit joking around already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.44,0:11:21.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.19,0:11:22.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.07,0:11:25.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A video phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.32,0:11:27.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.11,0:11:29.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The guy with the bombs on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:32.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's real!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.03,0:11:33.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shuu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.70,0:11:35.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:41.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,TRANS... FORM!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.84,0:11:51.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.80,0:11:54.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.39,0:11:58.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just mimicking the moves of these shirts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.10,0:12:00.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But nothing makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.10,0:12:06.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rather than doing things like that,\Nplease focus on finding the sender!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:08.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.15,0:12:09.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.53,0:12:12.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your movements just then reminded me of something...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:13.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.91,0:12:16.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.24,0:12:18.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} knows something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.75,0:12:21.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's gone off somewhere again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.13,0:12:26.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.63,0:12:28.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After you get the items from the customers...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.55,0:12:33.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You take them to the cashier's office back there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.30,0:12:34.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:37.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I'll say, "Please wait a moment."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.56,0:12:39.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for sharing that with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:41.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye then!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:47.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pardon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:49.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:50.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:51.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.86,0:12:54.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this is what the cashier's room is like!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.37,0:12:57.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:12:59.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me use your PC for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.12,0:13:01.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:06.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle Kogoro asked me to check something out...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:10.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About a snowy mountain disaster case from December 28th.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.55,0:13:13.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:20.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.93,0:13:22.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:29.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The case is from over ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.61,0:13:32.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like an experienced mountain climber...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.61,0:13:34.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got caught in an avalanche and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.55,0:13:39.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.20,0:13:41.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're done?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.79,0:13:46.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to tell Uncle Kogoro it was just as he thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:47.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:53.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Maruoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.05,0:13:59.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've pinpointed the sender's intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:04.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now I just need to figure out the bomber's aim...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.73,0:14:08.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did he have to cause all this commotion?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.94,0:14:12.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now all I can do is to wait for the bomber to make his next move.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.36,0:14:17.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, there's no mistaking that the bomber is very confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.45,0:14:21.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Confident that his crime from the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:25.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will never be found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.37,0:14:29.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.17,0:14:32.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.96,0:14:33.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.17,0:14:37.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, no one will find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.09,0:14:39.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My crime is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:41.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no evidence and not a single witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:45.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one threatening me is a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:48.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure they'll never be able to do this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:53.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, did he figure something out?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.11,0:14:54.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:14:57.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because of that brat fooling around...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:15:00.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't get my thinking straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.91,0:15:04.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh, so you're putting the blame on Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.50,0:15:09.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you had to go order sushi with that money...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:12.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're putting the blame on Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r} this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.46,0:15:13.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.88,0:15:16.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine, I'll think, I'll think!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.13,0:15:21.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:26.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, it was indeed snowy mountains...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.98,0:16:17.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why can't we go in?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.07,0:16:18.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We are not at liberty to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.99,0:16:27.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone took control of the floor with bombs?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.08,0:16:32.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, seems some fool's in there screwing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:34.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His demands were to find somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.88,0:16:41.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the guy that looks like Akai hasn't shown any signs of leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.05,0:16:43.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet he's stuck on that floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:56.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a hell of a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.07,0:16:59.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whether the bomber's caught or the bombs explode...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.69,0:17:02.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,People are gonna immediately rush out either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.74,0:17:06.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I doubt we'll be able to finish him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.41,0:17:08.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, this is even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.37,0:17:12.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The crowd will drown out the scent of our sniper.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:16.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And even should he wish to flee, he'll\Nno longer be able to move about freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.17,0:17:22.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For Chianti sniping from above and Korn\Nlooking on from the basement exit...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.72,0:17:24.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'll be easy prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.22,0:17:28.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, does he know about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.51,0:17:29.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"He"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.68,0:17:30.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:32.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bourbon, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.64,0:17:37.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard he started searching for the scientist,\NSherry, who betrayed the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.02,0:17:43.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who knows, he's a secretive one like Vermouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.53,0:17:46.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have no knowledge of his actions or whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:50.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, Bourbon hates Akai too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:53.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even more than Gin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:58.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, even if I knew where he was, I have\Nno intention of sharing any intel with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.42,0:18:00.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.92,0:18:04.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't believe Akai was dead from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.43,0:18:10.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He can't help but think he's the only one who could finish Akai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.35,0:18:13.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if that man turns out to be Akai...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.52,0:18:17.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'd let out his I-told-you-so snicker.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.48,0:18:22.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd rather not see him with that face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.16,0:18:33.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hurry up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.41,0:18:34.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.58,0:18:38.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How long is this gonna take?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.46,0:18:41.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you that famous detective, Mouri Kogoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:47.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and find the sender of those red\NT-shirts that the bomber's looking for...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.59,0:18:50.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that we may be released!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.35,0:18:51.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.60,0:18:57.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The identities of the sender and the\Nbomber are still a mystery to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:05.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't recognize the address...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:10.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:24.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.00,0:19:25.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a bomb next to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.17,0:19:28.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.01,0:19:30.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't allow the bombs to explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.47,0:19:36.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the name of the great detective, Mouri Kogoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.93,0:19:39.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you figured it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.39,0:19:42.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sender of the red underwear?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.48,0:19:45.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, you just said that it was a mystery to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.03,0:19:50.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, a mysterious sender and a mysterious bomber.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.37,0:19:54.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The key to solving this case is right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.62,0:20:00.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.62,0:20:02.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something's happening on that hijacked floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.96,0:20:08.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, looks like the great detective Mouri happens to be on that floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:09.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.17,0:20:10.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sleeping Korogou is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:14.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I do hope that he can prevent the explosion...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.81,0:20:17.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is stressful, but do your best, Detective Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.93,0:20:20.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you find it strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.35,0:20:25.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at the receipts that were sent with the red underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.82,0:20:36.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll see that they were all sold on a Sunday at\N12:28 in the fitness section of this department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.70,0:20:38.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he wanted to find the sender...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:43.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He would only need to wait secretly near\Nthat section at that time for them to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.17,0:20:47.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I bet the sender didn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.17,0:20:51.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why the bomber knocked out that man\Nin the restroom and strapped on the bombs...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.47,0:20:53.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And demanded the sender be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.68,0:20:55.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's exactly what's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.10,0:21:02.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To strap bombs onto someone, you need\Nto go somewhere to avoid people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.52,0:21:06.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But to do that, you'd have to take\Nyour eyes off the fitness section.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.27,0:21:10.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he was so desperate to find the\Nsender that he'd resort to bombs...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.32,0:21:13.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you think he'd do something this careless?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.41,0:21:17.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.20,0:21:21.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What if the bomber had an accomplice\Nto watch the fitness section for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.33,0:21:22.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.87,0:21:24.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take a look around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.17,0:21:31.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see how people are talking on their cell phones, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.63,0:21:35.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If our floor-hijacker had an accomplice...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.64,0:21:39.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't allow the customers to call.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.64,0:21:46.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, he probably strapped the bombs to\Nthat man long before 12:28 for preparation?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.19,0:21:50.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, the bombs were his last resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.82,0:21:56.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bombs he had left by the exits to this floor,\Nhe could easily retrieve them before explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.49,0:21:59.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if he doesn't know whether the sender would really come...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.91,0:22:03.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd be too risky for him to strap the bombs to someone prematurely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.42,0:22:09.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, you're saying the bomber is alone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.84,0:22:13.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could he not take his eyes off that section...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.01,0:22:15.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And still manage to strap bombs around that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.84,0:22:18.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bombs weren't strapped to him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.30,0:22:20.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those were already strapped before he came.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.06,0:22:22.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Already strapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.35,0:22:25.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You aren't trying to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.02,0:22:27.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.52,0:22:31.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bomber...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.57,0:22:36.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The "ordinary citizen"?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.20,0:24:06.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you in such a hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.12,0:24:10.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that you're looking for the same person I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.92,0:24:12.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't, Shuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.13,0:24:14.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're targeting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.92,0:24:16.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.80,0:24:19.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akai Shuuichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.70,0:24:42.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.99,0:24:44.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lipstick
